的頂部0.6514便止蝕離場。"},{"pid":"711c5a12ad6dcd7f5fb441821e35ad514cf36b89","tid":2013282,"uid":29821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119c43754636adbb845b5f4ba2660f5da844eb72","tid":2013282,"uid":35330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntimeframe真係好難決定"},{"pid":"de19a093a1463c45f82fe0ffad9c922447289ff1","tid":2013282,"uid":60892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef061010b9ae158684373500b350b35c8d9cd1ca","tid":2013282,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1-audusd/2643208512627743/?av=1858365591112043&amp;eav=AfZsosZW0kG31ixOUJ7-WX0VOERG8RwVh-hNXARijw8RcRg_qqTCeRw-bTbxrEfUo8jgZNZNCrQnzqixgZR3DF8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1-audusd%2F2643208512627743%2F%3Fav%3D1858365591112043%26eav%3DAfZsosZW0kG31ixOUJ7-WX0VOERG8RwVh-hNXARijw8RcRg_qqTCeRw-bTbxrEfUo8jgZNZNCrQnzqixgZR3DF8E&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=82fa9557\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1-audusd/2643208512627743/?av=1858365591112043&amp;eav=AfZsosZW0kG31ixOUJ7-WX0VOERG8RwVh-hNXARijw8RcRg_qqTCeRw-bTbxrEfUo8jgZNZNCrQnzqixgZR3DF8E</a><br />\n<br />\n大戶價格陷阱系列之前幾個Trade plan分享都衝出匯市，結果反應很好，感謝大家支持。日後我會更多留意這些市場(有朋友甚至提議比特幣!)，發現有好的setup一定